text: Kāore i te whakaritea he ikiiki tāpiri, ā, kāore ngā tereina o-runga e tau ki Wembley, ā, ko ngā wāhi whakatū waka, ā, kāore i te wātea ki te papa ngā whakaritenga whakatū waka me te eke.

text: I te nuinga o te wā, ko te noho ki tētahi whenua kē mō te wā roa ka here i a koe ki te whiwhi i tētahi pane uruwhenua i mua.

text: Katoa ngā tereina, nā MetroPlus me Metro; Ko ngā tereina MetroPlus kei te pito o te tereina e tata ana ki Cape Town.

text: Ka whai wāhi atu te kato ki ngā pūnaha mauranga. Ko te nuiga ka amuamu mō ngā pūnaha mauranga.
translated_text: Maori: Ka whai wāhi atu te kato ki ngā pūnaha mauranga. Ko te nuiga ka amuamu mō ngā pūnaha mauranga. English: I am a man of the world. I am a man of the world.

text: I te mea kua itiiti nei te rahinga tāngata, kāore he tino raruraru o te parakino-raiti, ā, ka manawareka anō hoki koe ki ngā whetū.
translated_text: Maori: I te mea kua itiiti nei te rahinga tāngata, kāore he tino raruraru o te parakino-raiti, ā, ka manawareka anō hoki koe ki ngā whetū. text: Ka rerekē ngā hiahia pane uruwhenua me ngā utu mai i tētahi whenua ki tētahi atu, ā, ka pāngia koe e ai ki tō whenua tipu.

text: I te nuinga o te wā, kāore he paku take o te rapu noa i ngā hekenga utu mō ngā tūru pakihi, karaehe-tuatahi rānei ki ngā rerenga tōtika i A ki B.
translated_text: Maori: I te nuinga o te wā, kāore he paku take o te rapu noa i ngā hekenga utu mō ngā tūru pakihi, karaehe-tuatahi rānei ki ngā rerenga tōtika i A ki B. English: I will not go with you, because I am not a good person.

text: He pukenga kei roto i te whiu taipere e hiahiatia nei e te hunga tūruhi.
translated_text: Maori: He pukenga kei roto i te whiu taipere e hiahiatia nei e te hunga tūruhi. English: I will go to the seashore and I will wash my clothes. Maori: He will go to the seashore and he will wash his clothes.

text: Ehara tēnei rerenga i te kōwhiringa kotahi ki te hiahia koe ki te hiki i te Tonga o te Moana nui a Kiwa me te tai uru o Amerika ki te Tonga. (tirohia ki raro)
translated_text: Maori: Ehara tēnei rerenga i te kōwhiringa kotahi ki te hiahia koe ki te hiki i te Tonga o te Moana nui a Kiwa me te tai uru o Amerika ki te Tonga. (tirohia ki raro) English: The Ehara Te Wairanga i te Rerenga i te Tonga is the name of the islands of the South Pacific.

text: Kua whakawhanaketia e San Francisco te hanganga tūruhi rahi whai i ngā tini hōtēra, whare kai, whare hui kounga anō hoki.
